    <listitem><para>Examples: [https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/qpid/trunk/qpid/ruby/examples/ | https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/qpid/trunk/qpid/ruby/examples/]</para></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</listitem>
<listitem>
  <para>.NET (AMQP 0-10):</para>
